::DrillBit::

Drillbit was looking at the new bot, and didn't see Stegotron and
Tricerodon sneek up on them. The grenades struck him, blasting him to
the ground, a few feet away.
"Aaaaaarrrrrrrrrggggggg!!!!" He screamed out in pain. It hurt like hell.
All he could do was crawl into position, and open gattaling gun fire, on
the Dinobots.
